  "author": "@Xovian",
  "text": "For any newbs, just some additional food for thought:\n\nEarly game, using all 4 characters with DeusEX can be useful, since setup on the first turn (especially with units that trend towards higher cost cards: +3 or more) can be very useful. \nThere is better later on of course, but for newbies that recently unlocked it, its something to consider for at least a couple units if nothing else. May not seem like much but it can really get the tempo going in a match early on.\n\nLove using Medicine on characters like Tawil or Saya, for some characters like these, it can be quite the game changer later on, so Covenants can definitly impact the game beyond mere RNG stat sticks.\n\nSo, dont forget to work on em as your able to do so.",
